query:
SELECT
                e.embed_type AS "embed_type:EmbedType",
                COUNT(DISTINCT e.*) AS embed_count,
                COUNT(DISTINCT eo.url) AS unique_origin_count,
                COUNT(eo.url) AS total_deployments
            FROM
                embed e
                LEFT JOIN embed_origin eo ON e.id = eo.embed_id
            WHERE
                e.organization_id = $1
            GROUP BY
                e.embed_type;
